originalText.text:
My dog and I had an excellent experience with Dr Jung. My dog somehow fractured her tooth and damaged another. Not only did we get a consultation with Dr Jung within a few weeks, we were able to get the surgery done with in a month of me first reaching out to the clinic to book the appointment!
Dr Jung did everything he could to make my dog (and me!) feel comfortable. He walked me through all the options and always made sure to answer all of my questions. During the surgery, Dr Jung contacted me with updates and made sure that I knew what was going on. The clinic also called me afterwards to follow about my dog's recovery.
I cannot recommend Dr Jung enough!
